java.awt.Component

lubiku.castleQuest.View.GamePanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, Runnable, Accessible
public class GamePanel extends JPanel implements Runnable

GamePanel

The GamePanel class is a JPanel subclass that represents the main game panel where the gameplay is rendered and updated.
